trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink"></xref> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink"> </xref> Web serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control creates a link for the client browser to navigate to another Web page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontrollen oppretter en kobling for klientleseren til å navigere til en annen side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The HyperLinkDesigner class provides design-time support for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen HyperLinkDesigner gir støtte for utforming for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method returns the markup that is used to render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden returnerer markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontroll på utformingstidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> method is called when there is a change to the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>metoden kalles når det er en endring i den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control or a copy of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontroll eller en kopi av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HyperLinkDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to render the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method generates the design-time markup for the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetDesignTimeHtml genererer utformingen markup for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>

trans-unit.source: The method first saves local copies of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.Text%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.NavigateUrl%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.ImageUrl%2A> properties, as well as the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> child collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden først lagrer lokale kopier av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.Text%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.NavigateUrl%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.ImageUrl%2A>Egenskaper, i tillegg til <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>underordnede samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.ImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.NavigateUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: It provides default values for these properties if the original values are `null` or blank.
trans-unit.target: Det gir standardverdier for disse egenskapene hvis de opprinnelige verdiene er `null` eller tom.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method then calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TextControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> base method to generate the markup and restores the properties and child control collection to their original values, if necessary.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetDesignTimeHtml kaller deretter den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TextControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>basere metode for å generere koden og gjenoppretter egenskapene og underordnet kontrollsamling de opprinnelige verdiene om nødvendig.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TextControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string containing the markup used to render the associated hyperlink control at design time.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder markup brukes til å gjengi tilknyttede hyperlink kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Called when there is a change to the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når det er en endring i den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The OnComponentChanged method is called when the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control is raised.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnComponentChanged kalles når den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>hendelse for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontrollen aktiveres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: Typically, this is in response to a property change on the control (for example, a **Properties** grid change).
trans-unit.target: Dette er vanligvis som svar på en endring av kontrollen (for eksempel en **Egenskaper** rutenett endre).

trans-unit.source: The OnComponentChanged creates a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs> object, and then calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> base method.
trans-unit.target: OnComponentChanged oppretter en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs>objektet, og deretter kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>basere metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The object that is the source of the event.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som er kilde for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs"></xref> object that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs"> </xref> objekt som inneholder Hendelsesdata.
